109
00:07:50,199 --> 00:07:53,487
Yeah, I never thought you married well.

110
00:07:53,898 --> 00:07:55,636
Lex, on the other hand,

111
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:57,667
received his genes from a

112
00:07:57,721 --> 00:08:00,105
