You know, all this baby stuff
is easier than people say.

153
00:10:05,131 --> 00:10:07,139
I think I pretty much
got it under control.

154
00:10:09,357 --> 00:10:10,062
Oh...

155
00:10:12,316 --> 00:10:13,725
Nice aim, little guy.

156
