something worthy of a captain of industry?

183
00:12:07,315 --> 00:12:09,985
I'm simply continuing
where you left off, dad.

184
00:12:10,161 --> 00:12:12,463
I, uh, can't talk now.

185
00:12:12,768 --> 00:12:13,543
Well,

186
00:12:13,684 --> 00:12:14,987
